race.comment: JUST A PRINCESS (2) was on speed throughout but collided in the run and finished second (28.16) at this track over 488m in a Maiden. Looks the one to beat on best. DODGY SHADOW (1) finished in the minors last time when second (28.13) at this track making it two minors from two runs. Overdue for a win and rates a key chance this line-up.    RATTLE YOUR DAGS (8) makes debut for the Justin Wood kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run. Something for the Multiples: WEST ON RICKY (7)
